      "content": "Powerhouse draws inspiration from blockchain's immutability principle. Through event sourcing, every state change is preserved as an append-only event, ensuring transparent, auditable histories. Unlike blockchain's global consensus which can limit speed and scalability, Powerhouse prioritizes local-first workflows so contributors can operate efficiently without requiring global synchronization.",
